{"tid":939973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有線］日本安川電機：華為近日突然叫停原本所有訂單","createTime":"2018-12-13T14:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T16:59:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6011aa463545405a13e939dd8977a083fa972c52","tid":939973,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:03:49.000Z","msg":"華為引發的國家安全問題，未有因為孟晚舟獲准保釋而降溫。<br />\n<br />\n日經新聞報道，軟銀計劃將旗下 4G 網絡的華為設備，全部換走，改用諾基亞及愛立信。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府日前已經決定，以安全為由，停向華為及中興購買通訊設備。<br />\n<br />\n華為表明，用一切辦法外向證明華為安全可靠。<br />\n<br />\n而有向華為出售製造機械的日本安川電機負責人則表示，華為近日突然叫停原本所有訂單，未知原因。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#華為　#icablenews　#hknews　#cablenews　#newsdaily　#news　#叫停<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1016259721899429/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1016259721899429%2F&d=YucF8bmLBH1D1PshIAAR97IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=be2ed363\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1016259721899429/</a>"},{"pid":"88c75cb679470fb49592eb76b4b2bde0d2b05c49","tid":939973,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"華為：依家係我唔賣，有生意都唔想做"},{"pid":"9d281b2f1247a69357396dfa1940c3d2128e153d","tid":939973,"uid":184103,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"88c75cb679470fb49592eb76b4b2bde0d2b05c49","tid":939973,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"華為：依家係我唔賣，有生意都唔想做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"53540fcf5eb6fafe2955bb4a1c1e649d6ae98269","tid":939973,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d281b2f1247a69357396dfa1940c3d2128e153d","tid":939973,"uid":184103,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"88c75cb679470fb49592eb76b4b2bde0d2b05c49","tid":939973,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"華為：依家係我唔賣，有